metadata.name: Traditionalism
metadata.description:
পটচিত্র | Potochitro


Art that speaks of how cultures amalgamate,
Stories of artists from old age,
How the father goes fishing to feed the child,
Child's playtime with mud and clay-

The wife's daily cooking experience,
The brother's journey to harvest honey,
From a forest of tigers-
Will he return home today?

Walking miles no complains,
Winnowing the husks away for money,
Forever feeding on the remains,
This is idea behind my Rare Pepe.
